{"tid":1474114,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求 想問物理治療轉介信！！","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:35:28.000Z","uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab02fe6760ac32de0dfcacce69fafb321d2e2469","tid":1474114,"uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"條腰本身有側彎 同埋有椎間盤突出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咗兩年私家物理治療 因為太貴。。<br />\n真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前問過一兩間診所想攞轉介信去睇政府物理治療，但係佢哋嗰度唔肯開俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係咪因為我個樣唔夠痛，定係佢哋覺得我講大話？<br />\n所以成日都開止痛藥比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴打絲打，有冇邊間診所係真係可以開物理治療轉介信俾我？<br />\n最好唔好太貴就得，近九龍區都可以。<br />\n感謝！想快啲去排政府物理治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712e91946244a03a20775262fc8e235fd25268cc","tid":1474114,"uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"跪求 <br />\n自推<br />\n818～"},{"pid":"fbb27fce875c77794b71931bc751beb920772692","tid":1474114,"uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"跪求 <br />\n自推<br />\n818～"},{"pid":"50919621fa711d440a74141270f959b1077dc839","tid":1474114,"uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"跪求 <br />\n自推<br />\n818～"},{"pid":"0a06487761d7568a89721f2987847487a8a327f7","tid":1474114,"uid":305324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"袁子威"},{"pid":"c92f976958b9aed56e9ffa08cbe4549a5f026f51","tid":1474114,"uid":162278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a06487761d7568a89721f2987847487a8a327f7","tid":1474114,"uid":305324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:1